text: André Ghem and Tristan Lamasine were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. David Pérez Sanz and Max Schnur won the title after defeating Steven de Waard and Andreas Mies in the final, 6–4, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Tampere Open - Doubles 2016 Men's Doubles
